{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.1","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:1","prev_osis_id":"Mic.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Promesses de restauration<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. \u00c9s 2:2-5; 60:1, etc.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Il arrivera, dans la suite des temps,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Que la montagne de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Sera fond\u00e9e sur le sommet des montagnes,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019elle s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8vera par-dessus les collines,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que les peuples y afflueront.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.2","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.3.12","name":"Mich\u00e9e 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.2","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:2","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Des nations s\u2019y rendront en foule, et diront:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Venez, et montons \u00e0 la montagne de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A la maison du Dieu de Jacob,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Afin qu\u2019il nous enseigne ses voies,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que nous marchions dans ses sentiers.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car de Sion sortira la loi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et de J\u00e9rusalem la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.3","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.3","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:3","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il sera le juge d\u2019un grand nombre de peuples,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u2019arbitre de nations puissantes, lointaines.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">De leurs glaives ils forgeront des hoyaux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et de leurs lances des serpes;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Une nation ne tirera plus l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e contre une autre,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et l\u2019on n\u2019apprendra plus la guerre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.2","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.4","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:4","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Ils habiteront chacun sous sa vigne et sous son figuier,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et il n\u2019y aura personne pour les troubler;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car la bouche de l\u2019\u00c9ternel des arm\u00e9es a parl\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.3","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.5","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:5","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Tandis que tous les peuples marchent, chacun au nom de son dieu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Nous marcherons, nous, au nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A toujours et \u00e0 perp\u00e9tuit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.6","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:6","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-8: cf. (J\u00e9 30:18-22. \u00c9z 34:12-16.) Za 9:9, 10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>En ce jour-l\u00e0, dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, je recueillerai les boiteux,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je rassemblerai ceux qui \u00e9taient chass\u00e9s,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ceux que j\u2019avais maltrait\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.7","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.7","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:7","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>\n    Des boiteux je ferai un reste,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">De ceux qui \u00e9taient chass\u00e9s une nation puissante;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et l\u2019\u00c9ternel r\u00e9gnera sur eux, \u00e0 la montagne de Sion,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">D\u00e8s lors et pour toujours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.8","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.8","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:8","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et toi, tour du troupeau, colline de la fille de Sion,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">A toi viendra, \u00e0 toi arrivera l\u2019ancienne domination,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Le royaume de la fille de J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.9","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.7","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.9","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:9","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Captivit\u00e9 et d\u00e9livrance<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-14: cf. J\u00e9 29:10-14. Za 12:2-6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Pourquoi maintenant pousses-tu des cris?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">N\u2019as-tu point de roi, plus de conseiller,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour que la douleur te saisisse comme une femme qui accouche?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.10","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.8","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.10","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:10","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Fille de Sion, souffre et g\u00e9mis comme une femme qui accouche!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car maintenant tu sortiras de la ville et tu habiteras dans les champs,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et tu iras jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Babylone;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u00e0 tu seras d\u00e9livr\u00e9e,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est l\u00e0 que l\u2019\u00c9ternel te rach\u00e8tera de la main de tes ennemis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.11","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.9","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.11","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:11","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Maintenant plusieurs nations se sont rassembl\u00e9es contre toi:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Qu\u2019elle soit profan\u00e9e, disent-elles,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que nos yeux se rassasient dans Sion!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.12","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.10","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.12","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:12","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Mais elles ne connaissent pas les pens\u00e9es de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elles ne comprennent pas ses desseins,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Elles ignorent qu\u2019il les a rassembl\u00e9es comme des gerbes dans l\u2019aire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.13","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.11","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.13","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:13","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Fille de Sion, l\u00e8ve-toi et foule!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je te ferai une corne de fer et des ongles d\u2019airain,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et tu broieras des peuples nombreux;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu consacreras leurs biens \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Leurs richesses au Seigneur de toute la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.14","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.12","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.14","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 4:14","prev_osis_id":"Mic.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Maintenant, fille de troupes, rassemble tes troupes!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">On nous assi\u00e8ge;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Avec la verge on frappe sur la joue le juge d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.4.13","name":"Mich\u00e9e 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbd6c6f47.68699363');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbd6c6f47.68699363\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbd6c6f47.68699363","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbd6c6f47.68699363'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbd6c6f47.68699363\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}